                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1867-18350817 t18350817-1867-punishment-142"></join>Transported for life</rs>.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury on account of his character, and the Prosecutor's taking so large a discount.</hi>
